Package com.aep.model

Class AcademicProfessionalDTO

java.lang.Object
com.aep.model.AcademicProfessionalDTO
public class AcademicProfessionalDTO extends Object
AcademicProfessionalDTO represents an academic professional in the system. It serves as a Data Transfer Object for the AcademicProfessional table.
